snippet.title: Super Power Racing Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Power Racing is a 90s top arcade racer inspired by Super Sprint and Ridge Racer.

It's available now to wishlist on Steam.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2377720/Super_Power_Racing/
